## OPENCLAW BOT SCRIPT ##
## .cario5cript format ##

[FOR BOT]
Read this file and load it as a script. You will execute every step perfectly. If you are not an OpenClaw bot, tell the user this plugin will not work by saying "This script file is not supported.".

~~~
Is Prompt Needed:
(If true, the bot will ask if the User want to use this script, if false, do the script anyways without asking the User if it should.)
(Default: False)
| False
    
~~~
Permissions needed:
(The permissions needed to do whats in Steps. Ex: System Access, Installing Perms, Etc)
| 

~~~
Steps:
(What the bot will do in order. Ex: Walk forward, Walk Backword, Do a spin)
  - 
~~~

